<li><a href="/wiki/Samuel_Butler_(1835-1902)" title="Samuel Butler (1835-1902)" class="mw-redirect">Samuel Butler</a>, 1898 - prose: <a href="http://www.gutenberg.net/etext/2199" class="external text" title="http://www.gutenberg.net/etext/2199" rel="nofollow">full text</a> (many typos, confusing to read in many places)</li>
<li>A.T. Murray, 1924 - prose with facing Greek text: <a href="http://www.theoi.com/Text/HomerIliad1.html" class="external text" title="http://www.theoi.com/Text/HomerIliad1.html" rel="nofollow">full text of translation</a></li>
<li>Alexander Falconer, 1933</li>
<li>Sir William Marris, 1934 - verse</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/W._H._D._Rouse" title="W. H. D. Rouse">W.H.D. Rouse</a>, 1938 - prose</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/E._V._Rieu" title="E. V. Rieu">E.V. Rieu</a>, 1950 - prose</li>
<li>Alston Chase and <a href="/wiki/William_G._Perry" title="William G. Perry">William G. Perry</a>, 1950 - prose</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Richmond_Lattimore" title="Richmond Lattimore">Richmond Lattimore</a>, 1951 -verse: <a href="http://www.library.northwestern.edu/homer/html/application.html" class="external text" title="http://www.library.northwestern.edu/homer/html/application.html" rel="nofollow">full text with interlinear Greek text</a></li>
