<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Iliad&amp;action=edit&amp;section=21" title="Edit section: References">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">References</span></h2>
<div class="references-small" style="margin-left:1.5em;">
